{"tid":541673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得左可以代替咗嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-01-26T16:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T16:56:05.000Z","uid":118469,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c749b503dc5eae2adc186700b4e7360f7eb1bb21","tid":541673,"uid":118469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"我依家屌撚醒晒你地<br />\n明知 咗 依個正字點解重要用 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地話用 左 方便啲<br />\n噉你地同用 法覺=發覺 吾=唔 有乜分別咪又係5p字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好笑係重要屌返屌錯字嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講唔知以為上咗5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能你地會話錯字唔係討論嘅核心<br />\n但係唔好將你地嘅錯誤當作正確或者正常得唔得<br />\n錯咪改囉。依家返多個口字邊有幾難呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌返屌錯字嘅人唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔識字嘅唔好學人上網</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我只係睇唔過眼依家啲人錯字重大條道理咁屌人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca0ee7996866e20de756c777b4257083cac01d8","tid":541673,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1f1a7c32359abbea4ca50504c8ff34f4f052989","tid":541673,"uid":168771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"廣東話萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm